<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>C3 Pemulihan GPT</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@picocss/pico@2/css/pico.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #ffffff; /* White background */
      color: #d1cece; /* Dark gray text color */
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif; /* Default font */
      padding: 20px; /* Add some padding */
    }
    header {
      text-align: center; /* Center align header content */
      margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add margin below header */
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333333; /* Dark gray heading color */
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6; /* Increase line height for better readability */
      color: #333333;
    }
    form {
      margin-top: 20px; /* Add margin above form */
    }
    button {
      background-color: #007bff; /* Blue button background */
      color: #ffffff; /* White button text color */
      border: none; /* Remove button border */
      padding: 10px 20px; /* Add padding inside button */
      cursor: pointer; /* Change cursor to pointer on hover */
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease; /* Smooth transition for background color */
    }
    button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3; /* Darker blue on hover */
    }
    h2 {
      color: #000000; /* Black heading color */
      margin-top: 20px; /* Add margin above response header */
    }
    p.response {
      background-color: #f0f0f0; /* Light gray background for response */
      padding: 10px; /* Add padding around response */
      border-radius: 5px; /* Rounded corners */
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <img src="/logo4.png" alt="" class="animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">
  </header>
  <h1 class="animate__animated animate__bounce">AI Chat - Q&A</h1>
  <p class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn">Gereja C3 Pemulihan Kupang menyediakan fitur AI chat yang bermanfaat bagi jemaat yang ingin tahu informasi spesifik mengenai jadwal ibadah di gereja C3 Pemulihan.</p>
  <form action="/chat" method="POST">
    <label style="color: #333333;" for="message">Masukkan pertanyaan Anda:</label><br>
    <input style="background-color: #d1cece; color: #333333;" type="text" id="message" name="message" required placeholder="silahkan bertanya 😁😇..."><br><br>
    <button type="submit" class="animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">Kirim</button>
  </form>

  <% if (response) { %>
    <h2 class="animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">Respon dari AI:</h2>
    <p class="response animate__animated animate__fadeInUp"><%= response %></p>
  <% } %>
</body>
</html>
